b'@NetflixIndia @JhulanG10 @OfficialCSFilmz @prosit_roy #KarneshSSharma #AbhishekBanerjee @manojmittra @saurabh0903 @rajneesh_chopra #RaviKiranAyyagari #MeenalAgarwal @veerakapur7 @Harry0073 @iamkeitan @shashwatology @vfx_redchillies #AntiCasting #AnkitMalik'
b"As a cricketing nation, we have to give our women cricketers their due. Jhulan's story is truly an underdog story in the history of cricket in India and the film is our celebration of her spirit."

b"It is their hard work, passion & their undefeated mission to bring attention to women's cricket that has turned around things for generations to come. As a woman, I was proud to hear Jhulan's story & it is an honour for me to try & bring her life to audiences & cricket lovers."

b'There is still a lot of work to be done and we have to empower them with the best so that the sport can flourish for women in India.\n\nWe should all salute Jhulan and her team-mates for revolutionizing women\xe2\x80\x99s cricket in India.'

b'Her life is a living testimony that passion and perseverance triumphs over any or all adversities and Chakda Xpress is the most definitive look into the not so rosy world of women\xe2\x80\x99s cricket back then.'

b'Jhulan had a fighting and extremely uncertain cricketing career and she stayed motivated to make her country proud. She strived to change the stereotype that women can\xe2\x80\x99t make a career out of playing cricket in India so that the next generation of girls had a better playing field.'

b'From support systems, to facilities, to having a stable income from playing the game, to even having a future in cricket \xe2\x80\x93 very little propelled women of India to take up cricket as a profession.'

b'At a time when Jhulan decided to become a cricketer and make her country proud on the global stage, it was very tough for women to even think of playing the sport. This film is a dramatic retelling of several instances that shaped her life and also women\xe2\x80\x99s cricket.'

b'It is a really special film because it is essentially a story of tremendous sacrifice. Chakda Xpress is inspired by the life and times of former Indian captain Jhulan Goswami and it will be an eye-opener into the world of women\xe2\x80\x99s cricket. https://t.co/eRCl6tLvEu'
